{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And the whole wedding night, he [? wept ?] through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And that's when I realized that he was not, not quite right, that he was a sick man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And he, then he-- it turned out later, and that I only found out 15 years later-- that he actually was a schizophrenic, and that he already had treatment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "He had already electroshock treatment before that, during the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "He was in hiding there for awhile, but that he had some electroshock treatment, that he was a sick man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And so anyway, we were married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And then he, he couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And he wanted to go back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And eventually, there was an audition for a South-- a job in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And he eventually got the job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And when he got the contract, he said that he's schizophrenic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And he can't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "He's mad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And he can't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And I spoke to a fr-- a friend who was a psychiatrist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And he said, you have two choices.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Either you keep through with him here and you get him-- we get him into mental hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "But since you haven't got a penny to your name, they won't treat him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And they will-- you will never get there-- from out of there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "Or you try and get him onto the boat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "He had a priority passage to go to South Africa-- if I get him onto the boat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "It's your decision.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "Well, I decided that I give him a chance, this chance, and get him onto the boat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And so-- but he did all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "He did suicide attempts, one after the other, but always make sure that he shouldn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
